<br>
If it takes 1.5 seconds to use all 3 charges of a T-rod, which takes 4.5 seconds to cast, then you're looking at 43 mana per second.  (260mana/6seconds)<br>
<br>
A two charge mod rod that takes 4 seconds to cast and 1.5 seconds to use would be able to exchange at only 18.2 mana per second.  (100mana/5.5seconds)<br>
<br>
More mana per second tends to be more convenient, especially for raids and as levels increase.<br>
